                      "
                    >
                      Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,
                    </p>

                    <p
                      style="
                        font-size: 16px;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
                      "
                    >
                      Thanks for signing up! To complete your account setup,
                      please verify your email address by clicking the button
